Classes table (Name of Table is the class e.g: CCS 224):
    Student ID
    Student First Name
    Student Surname
    Classes attended(Want it to auto increment every time the student is in class )
    Teacher in charge of class
    Total classes(Want it to auto increment every time a class occurs)

Teachers table (Name of the Table is the teacher's name e.g Mr. Moturi)
    Classes they're teaching

Students table (Name of the Table is the Student's name)
    Classes they're taking


